{"tid":1165674,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"彭定康：修例是1997年以來最差的事","createTime":"2019-05-22T02:58:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-22T03:59:48.000Z","uid":20933,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ca7a9dc198ef600a0a88e6edf3616c0952659662","tid":1165674,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T02:58:30.000Z","msg":"政府修訂《逃犯條例》爭議不絕，前港督彭定康周二（21日）出席英國倫敦一個活動時發言，形容修例是香港自1997年回歸以來「最差的事」。<br />\n<br />\n彭定康又稱，修例打破了中央對港的「一國兩制」承諾，並威脅香港作為國際金融中心的地位：「如果中央看待香港就像看待深圳、上海一樣，只是把香港當作內地一部分，那麽國際社會未來將會有『香港似乎已經不再特別』的想法」。<br />\n<br />\n彭定康亦警告，根據內地「依法而治」（rule by law）的制度，黨、法庭和執法部門之間其實並無分別，如果政府通過修例，中國內地與香港之間的防火牆將被移除，香港市民便有可能承受內地「依法而治」的風險。"},{"pid":"f2c6874dda2bbb8a2557737046e4d90dcb86bae0","tid":1165674,"uid":20933,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T02:58:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190522/s00001/1558491954346/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190522%2Fs00001%2F1558491954346%2F&d=ruuHvkpDPTXA%2B6q4k3%2F6TaVNHo2TAuuzEKoC36QvVjA%3D&h=5816ac97\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190522%2Fs00001%2F1558491954346%2F&h=57c0ed50\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190522/s00001/1558491954346/</a>"},{"pid":"7b164826b3e05ca762b8a9d1d971ac21a398d7fa","tid":1165674,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T03:38:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5833d90de8a1a9796551d328f8833bf0eba0693d","tid":1165674,"uid":231583,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T03:56:59.000Z","msg":"英國：一國兩制運作良好"},{"pid":"c3afe1385e940613ea19620d3ed7be5f90930186","tid":1165674,"uid":149026,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T03:58:24.000Z","msg":"【民陣6.9反惡法遊行】 <br />\n日期：6月9日（日）<br />\n集合地點：銅鑼灣東角道<br />\n時間：下午2時30分集合，3時正起步<br />\n遊行路線：銅鑼灣東角道遊行至金鐘添美道立法會"},{"pid":"556d677ed718d12768f79a1449ae03fda681b7b5","tid":1165674,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T03:59:09.000Z","msg":"陸續有來"},{"pid":"18f1178cb9b325d74dd008ae767b8b907660d708","tid":1165674,"uid":28831,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T03:59:20.000Z","msg":"過幾年送幾個鬼佬返支那<br />\n：「是1997年以來最差的事」<br />\n再過幾年取消特衰護照<br />\n：「是1997年以來最差的事」<br />\n再過幾年拆關<br />\n：「是1997年以來最差的事」"},{"pid":"99b238af75aadb34e637027cee8887530520c5e1","tid":1165674,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T03:59:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T5pxTPy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT5pxTPy.jpg&h=605671df&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}